description: Some mothers say that they are surprised how I combine being and trying to make art right in the living environment. For me and my second child, Savva, it seemed like there was no choice left, not to try to do something, because he gives me a lot of joy and free space, he can play alone for a long time or look out the window at the bulldozer, he can laugh and jump on my back , he can tell me every little thing that I am great and that I am super. He's my best postpartum antidepressant.
